sentences: In 2002, Fauna lived in the exurb community of Indio, California.
In 2007, uncertain began as the solo project of Florian-Ayala Fauna.

It often involved field recordings, processed sounds, and tape loops while their current cycle (since 2012) features albums about a family of foxes done with composition, sampling, and complex music production on Ableton Live and Kontakt.
As of 2016, Fauna is the main producer and collaborates with others, primarily with Felix Keigh who is her fianc√© and main vocalist.

In August 2016, The Public's Cory Perla described both her art and music as "otherworldly."

In March 2017, British music magazine The Quietus's Russell Cuzner summed up her music as "somehow fulfil[s] a similar aesthetic to the artist's equally prolific visual art that often depict animal heads [...] as if charged with some kind of hidden power, part gothic horror, part Gnostic totem."
In December 2019, Columbus Alive's Andy Downing said God Is a Man Eater was "dense, buzzing, six-track song cycle."
